Java 11 Features:
1. Added new methods in String class such as isBlank, lines, strip, stripLeading, stripTrailing and repeat.
2. Added readString and writeString static methods in Files class.
3. Added local variable syntax in lambda expression
4. Added Optional object new method isEmpty
5. Added HTTP Client API that makes http request.
6. Run and execute java program without compilation

Java 17 Features:
1. Added method to convert Collection to Array
2. Sealed classes
3. Pattern matching for switch
4. Restore always-strict floating-point semantics
5. enhanced pseudo-random number generator